      <title>博客搭建教程</title>
      <link href="/2021/09/10/blog-tutorial/"/>
      <url>/2021/09/10/blog-tutorial/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>xxx</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="博客搭建教程"><a href="#博客搭建教程" class="headerlink" title="博客搭建教程"></a>博客搭建教程</h1><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/102592286">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/102592286</a></p><h2 id="1-准备工作"><a href="#1-准备工作" class="headerlink" title="1. 准备工作"></a>1. 准备工作</h2><ol><li><p>注册github账号; 安装git; 本地生成ssh key 添加至github账户</p></li><li><p>安装node.js <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">https://nodejs.org/en/</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1、打开文件夹</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     cd /usr/tools</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2、创建文件夹</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     mkdir node</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(后续操作在此目录：/usr/tools/node)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">3、下载node资源</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v13.6.0/node-v13.6.0-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">4、解压文件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     tar -xf node-v13.6.0-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">5、改名</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">　 mv node-v13.6.0-linux-x64  v13.6.0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">6、创建软连接</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     ln -s /usr/tools/node/v13.6.0/bin/npm /usr/local/bin/</span><br><span class="line">     ln -s /usr/tools/node/v13.6.0/bin/node /usr/local/bin/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">7、查询版本号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   node -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">　 npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>创建仓库 仓库名应该为：<strong>用户名</strong>.github.io 这个<strong>用户名</strong>使用你的GitHub帐号名称代替，这是固定写法; settings 页面底端出现 github pages  Your GitHub Pages site is currently being built from the <code>main</code> branch.说明建立成功 (必须公开项目)</p></li></ol><h2 id="2-正式搭建"><a href="#2-正式搭建" class="headerlink" title="2. 正式搭建"></a>2. 正式搭建</h2><ol><li><p>新建文件夹Blog ，进入该文件夹，之后的操作都是在该文件夹下</p></li><li><p>npm install -g hexo-cli ; 创建软连接ln -s /usr/tools/node/v13.6.0/bin/hexo /usr/local/bin/ 然后hexo -v 查看是否安装成功；</p></li><li><p>hexo init 初始化博客</p></li><li><p>hexo g 静态部署</p></li><li><p>hexo s 查看部署成功的网页;  <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http://baixin.io/2015/08/HEXO%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E4%BA%86">http://localhost:4000</a>  本地查看</p></li><li><p>将Hexo部署到github: 打开 _config.yml 文件 在文件底部添加</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: git@  #你的仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>回到 Blog 文件夹中，打开 Git Bash，安装Git部署插件，输入命令 npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</p></li><li><p>然后分别输入以下三条命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean   #清除缓存文件 db.json 和已生成的静态文件 public</span><br><span class="line">hexo g       #生成网站静态文件到默认设置的 public 文件夹(hexo generate 的缩写)</span><br><span class="line">hexo d       #自动生成网站静态文件，并部署到设定的仓库(hexo deploy 的缩写)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>完成以后，打开浏览器，输入 <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://fengye97.github.io/">https://xxx.github.io</a> 就可以打开你的网页了<a href="https://wsustcid.github.io/ws-garage.github.io/">https://wsustcid.github.io/ws-garage.github.io/</a></p></li><li><p>现在虽然可以访问我们的网站，但是网址是GitHub提供的：<a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http://xxxx.github.io">http://xxxx.github.io</a> 而我们想使用我们自己的个性化域名，这就需要绑定我们自己的域名。下一篇介绍解析域名和绑定域名。</p></li></ol><p>将My_Blog初始化为git项目，上传至github; 然后尝试从另一台电脑克隆本项目，看能否继续写博客</p><h2 id="3-解析域名"><a href="#3-解析域名" class="headerlink" title="3. 解析域名"></a>3. 解析域名</h2><ol><li>购买域名 <a href="https://wanwang.aliyun.com/%EF%BC%9B">https://wanwang.aliyun.com/；</a> <a href="https://dnspod.cloud.tencent.com/">https://dnspod.cloud.tencent.com/</a></li><li>解析域名 <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/103813944">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/103813944</a></li></ol><h2 id="4-个性化定制"><a href="#4-个性化定制" class="headerlink" title="4. 个性化定制"></a>4. 个性化定制</h2><ol><li><p>进入博客根目录文件夹，下载next主题至theme文件夹下: <code>git clone https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git</code> 下载后 删除next下的.git文件夹</p></li><li><p>```<br>打开根目录下的_config.yml(称为站点配置文件)，修改主题（注意冒号后都要有空格）：</p><h1 id="Site"><a href="#Site" class="headerlink" title="Site"></a>Site</h1><p>title: 枫叶苑  #标题<br>subtitle: ‘’<br>description: 选择有时候比努力更重要     #简介或者格言<br>keywords:<br>author: 枫叶     #作者<br>language: zh-CN     #主题语言<br>timezone: Asia/Shanghai    #中国的时区</p><h1 id="Extensions"><a href="#Extensions" class="headerlink" title="Extensions"></a>Extensions</h1><h2 id="Plugins-https-hexo-io-plugins"><a href="#Plugins-https-hexo-io-plugins" class="headerlink" title="Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/"></a>Plugins: <a href="https://hexo.io/plugins/">https://hexo.io/plugins/</a></h2><h2 id="Themes-https-hexo-io-themes"><a href="#Themes-https-hexo-io-themes" class="headerlink" title="Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/"></a>Themes: <a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></h2><p>theme: hexo-theme-next   #主题改为next</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">3. ```</span><br><span class="line">   打开目录Blog/themes/next/下的_config.yml（称为主题配置文件），只要将你选的主题前的#删除就行了：</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   # Schemes</span><br><span class="line">   #scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">   #scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">   #scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">   scheme: Gemini    #这是我选的主题</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>回到Blog根目录打开Git Bash，输入如下三条命令：</p><p>hexo clean<br>hexo g<br>hexo d</p></li></ol><h2 id="5-博客撰写"><a href="#5-博客撰写" class="headerlink" title="5. 博客撰写"></a>5. 博客撰写</h2><h4 id="1-command-line"><a href="#1-command-line" class="headerlink" title="1. command line"></a>1. command line</h4><blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;title&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><p>生成新文章在 \source_posts\title.md 用markdown编辑器打开可以编辑</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 文章标题  # 文章页面上的显示名称, 可以任意修改, 不会出现在URL中</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-02-02 20:13:14  # 文章生成时间, 一般不改</span><br><span class="line">categories: diary  # 文章分类目录, 多个分类使用[a,b,c]这种格式</span><br><span class="line">tags: [Hexo,diary]  # 文章标签</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#这里开始使用markdown格式输入你的正文.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#more标签以下的内容要点击“阅读全文”才能看见</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-Direct-Creation"><a href="#2-Direct-Creation" class="headerlink" title="2. Direct Creation"></a>2. Direct Creation</h4><p>也可以不使用命令自己创建 .md 文件，只需在文件开头手动加入如下格式 Front-matter 即可，写完后运行 <code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</code> 发布。</p><p>换电脑更新博客</p><p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/21193762">https://www.zhihu.com/question/21193762</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
